VR's fully immersive world.\n{2749921605164381}\n\n{1010189834052785}\n- Immersive VR Experience: Feel the excitement of kart racing with realistic sensations.\n- Thrilling Tracks: Test your skills on challenging tracks designed for strategy and precision.\n- Global Competition: Compete worldwide, climb leaderboards, and become the ultimate champion.\n- Customizable Karts: Personalize your kart with upgrades for better performance and appearance.\n- Intense Head-to-Head Races: Compete against AI and real players in adrenaline-pumping races.\n- Skill Mastery: Hone reflexes and focus to navigate sharp corners and lead the pack.\n- VR Enhancements: Heightened realism and immersion elevate your kart racing experience.\n\n{348264668061132}\n\nWhy Choose Kart 360 VR:\nEmbark on an exhilarating journey where each race is a challenge and victory makes you a legend. With stunning visuals and a true-to-life VR environment, Kart 360 VR is the definitive choice for racing enthusiasts and VR gamers alike.\n\n{797696912453103}", "short_description": "Strap into your VR headsets and dive into the adrenaline-pumping world of Kart 360 VR! Get ready for an unparalleled immersive kart racing experience where speed meets skill, and legends are forged in the heat of intense virtual competition."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://geniegaming.com/vr-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Genie Gaming Ltd", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://geniegaming.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "673385183287495"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, 